{
  "name": "Jolting Lightning Strum",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Taijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can see tension in the muscles and body of your friends and can release that tension with a single pressure point press. This jutsu cannot have its cost reduced by any means.</p><p>Select one willing creature other than you, who you can reach as you press a pressure point on their back. When you do you release a buildup of pooled chakra within them. Affected creature can spend up to two chakra die, regaining a number of chakra points equal to the result.</p><p>Additionally, for the duration the affected creature gains an additional use of any 1 class feature with a use limitation or 1 additional spendable resource. If this additional resource isn't spent by the end of the duration it is lost. (Ex. Actualization Die, Hunter Exploit, Brave Order, Preserve or Take Life, Chakra Recovery or Superiority Die etc.) A creature can only benefit from this effect of this jutsu once per short rest.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank or higher, you can target up to two creatures, instead of one. If this jutsu is Cast at A-Rank or higher, affected creatures instead regain 2 additional class features uses/resources.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
